314
00:30:49,200 --> 00:30:53,700
If we want to get to Yunhuang, who knows how many will make it there alive.

315
00:30:54,800 --> 00:30:58,200
We couldn't find anywhere to make money in the Central Plains.

316
00:30:58,200 --> 00:31:01,600
If we stayed there, we'd still be poor. We might as well go to Yunhuang.

317
00:31:01,600 --> 00:31:03,800
In the legends, Yunhuang is peaceful and beautiful.

318
00:31:03,800 --> 00:31:06,000
