364
00:34:26,480 --> 00:34:29,970
That's the legendary Jing Pagoda of Yunhuang, isn't it?

365
00:34:29,970 --> 00:34:33,410
I heard elders in my village say that it's about 64,000 feet tall.
(T/N: Chinese feet, one Chinese foot = 1/3 meter)

366
00:34:33,410 --> 00:34:35,480
It was built by Kongsang's Heavenly King.

367
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:38,070
But... it's so tall.

368
00:34:38,070 --> 00:34:40,750
How hard would it be to climb it?

