372
00:34:56,980 --> 00:34:59,720
Who can hear whose prayers?

373
00:35:01,660 --> 00:35:03,880
It's a legend.

374
00:35:05,350 --> 00:35:07,370
Hey, Brother Ice Cube!

375
00:35:07,370 --> 00:35:09,950
Brother Ice Cube, where are you going?

376
00:35:10,580 --> 00:35:12,580
You must be really powerful, right?

377
00:35:12,580 --> 00:35:16,840
I heard the village elders say that some people have divine powers and are very powerful.

378
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:20,120
You have divine powers, right? Take me there.

379
00:35:20,120 --> 00:35:22,370
Then, can I give you some of my fairy grass?

380
00:35:22,370 --> 00:35:27,200
Take me there. I promise that I won't talk to you and I won't annoy you.

381
00:35:27,200 --> 00:35:31,570
Yunhuang is a mythical place. There are never any battles there, I must go.

382
00:35:33,330 --> 00:35:35,440
