400
00:36:43,710 --> 00:36:48,020
In actuality, it seals the crown princess' heart.

401
00:36:48,020 --> 00:36:51,540
If the crown princess sincerely falls in love with someone,

402
00:36:51,540 --> 00:36:55,080
