403
00:36:56,560 --> 00:36:58,960
[Bai Ying - Reigning Princess Bai of Kongsang]

404
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:26,180
One hundred years ago, when I fell off the pagoda,

405
00:37:26,950 --> 00:37:29,570
I was rescued by the Earth Ring.

406
00:37:32,630 --> 00:37:37,200
Prince Zhen Lan fought to the death against Cangliu alone.

407
00:37:47,130 --> 00:37:51,740
By the time I woke from the Still Meditation and rushed to the battlefield,

408
00:37:51,740 --> 00:37:54,210
Prince Zhen Lan's power of Heaven

409
00:37:54,210 --> 00:37:57,740
