410
00:37:57,740 --> 00:38:00,110
There was no trace of it anywhere.

411
00:38:11,720 --> 00:38:15,820
Maybe... this is my fate.

412
00:38:17,290 --> 00:38:19,510
[Earth Ring]

413
00:38:26,040 --> 00:38:30,980
After Zhen Lan fell into a deep sleep, in order to protect the Kongsang people,

414
00:38:30,980 --> 00:38:35,940
the six princes sacrificed half of their spiritual powers to open up Wuse City.
 [Kongsang - Wuse City]

