418
00:39:28,610 --> 00:39:31,690
In this hundred years, I've gone across the whole of Yunhuang.

419
00:39:31,690 --> 00:39:34,410
But I still haven't found the Heavenly Ring.

420
00:39:34,410 --> 00:39:36,820
Or the sealed power of Heaven.

421
00:39:36,820 --> 00:39:40,070
But I've told you all about Yunhuang's land and culture.

422
00:39:40,070 --> 00:39:44,840
This time, I went to Banbu City in Kangping Province.

423
00:39:45,460 --> 00:39:50,510
Banbu City is a desert city. The houses there are made of rocks.

424
00:39:50,510 --> 00:39:52,520
Although I went at night,

425
00:39:52,520 --> 00:39:56,880
