431
00:40:31,720 --> 00:40:35,620
But it's already been a hundred years. There hasn't been any movement whatsoever.

432
00:40:36,190 --> 00:40:37,870
His Highness will wake up one day.

433
00:40:37,870 --> 00:40:41,220
A'Ying, it's been a hundred years already.
