446
00:41:37,090 --> 00:41:40,690
High Priest, why have you called me here so urgently?

447
00:41:40,690 --> 00:41:43,140
A'Ying, there's a change in the Greedy Wolf Star.

448
00:41:43,140 --> 00:41:45,660
A huge misfortune will fall upon the world soon.

449
00:41:45,660 --> 00:41:49,410
The invader will enter through Tianque into Yunhuang.

450
00:41:49,410 --> 00:41:53,600
