458
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:16,720
In that case, after dark

459
00:42:16,720 --> 00:42:19,490
I'll go to Tianque and find this invader.

460
00:42:19,490 --> 00:42:22,160
Maybe I can help them avoid the crisis.

461
00:42:22,160 --> 00:42:25,650
Reigning Princess, please be safe.

462
00:42:53,160 --> 00:42:56,250
No matter who it is, I hope this person

